      "updated": 1769697960971,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "heart signal (~1mV) : 0.03 - 80Hz\n                 +\nnoise (>20mV) :\n    Baseline wander <0.5/0.03Hz\n    mains hum 60Hz (common-mode V)\n    muscle noise > 40/80Hz",
      "fontSize": 14.48954378566956,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "heart signal (~1mV) : 0.03 - 80Hz\n                 +\nnoise (>20mV) :\n    Baseline wander <0.5/0.03Hz\n    mains hum 60Hz (common-mode V)\n    muscle noise > 40/80Hz",
